        Hurray! You're nearly all booked in to FINALLY understand accent work, feel connected to your own voice whilst expansive in the possibilities of what it can be. Part of a small supportive cohort of like-minded creatives with the opportunity to stretch your acting muscles and put the work into direct practice, receive clear and personalised feedback, get round to filming that ever-elusive spotlight material and know exactly what your next steps are. Congrats!! Just the next few points to check over to make sure you feel safe and seen and I can give you the best training possible.
