        <p>Sessions are delivered live online. Sessions will be recorded and made available to participants who miss a class. Recordings are for personal use only and must not be shared, distributed, or uploaded elsewhere. Access to recordings and course materials is provided for the duration of the module(s) you have booked.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">4. Community Guidelines</h2>
        <p>This programme is rooted in trust, respect, and collaboration. Participants are expected to: communicate kindly and professionally, respect differing experiences, identities, and vocal backgrounds. Maintain confidentiality around shared work and discussions. Any behaviour that compromises the safety or integrity of the group may result in removal from the programme without refund.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-bold mb-3">5. Payment &amp; Booking</h2>
        <p>All fees are payable in advance via Stripe. You may book one module, two modules, or the full programme. Your place is confirmed once payment is received. By completing payment, you confirm that you have read and agreed to these Terms &amp; Conditions.</p>
      </div>

