          <li>If you cancel within 14 days of the start date, a 50% refund will be offered.</li>
          <li>After the programme has started: once a module has begun, refunds are not available, as your place cannot be reallocated. You will still retain access to recordings and materials for the module you have joined.</li>
          <li>Should exceptional/unforeseen circumstances arise (e.g. serious illness), please contact me directly. Each situation will be considered with care and fairness.</li>
